{"uri": "at://did:plc:vywcppocpkrs3vrxo6b7xob3/app.bsky.feed.post/3mnxp3jgd7k2a", "parent_uri": null, "author_did": "did:plc:vywcppocpkrs3vrxo6b7xob3", "author_handle": "loudmouthkid62.bsky.social", "author_name": "@Loudmouthkid62", "text": "As my late combat veteran Purple Heart recipient father taught me,\n\n“When you ‘assume,’\nyou make an ‘ass’ out of ‘u’ and ‘me.’”\n\nSo you guessed wrong.\n\nDo you know the connection between artificial intelligence and data centers?", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T21:52:36.046Z", "likes": 0, "replies_count": 1, "reposts": 0, "depth": 0, "is_root": true}
